     66          // Each index of the event array maps 1-to-1 to the network index.
     67          // For multi-network and single network, we only allocate 1 copy
     68          // of the event (i.e. an array of element size 1). App Builder always defines
     69          // EMBER_AF_ZC_AND_ZR_DEVICE_COUNT to the correct value.
     70          
